\c 73
\p Bhuku 3
\p (Mapisarema 73 - 89 )
\s Mufaro wavakaipa ndowenguva duku
\d Pisarema raAsafi.
\p
\v 731 Zvirokwazvo Mwari anoitira Isiraeri zvakanaka,
\s Ivo vane mwoyo yakachena.
\p
\v 2 Asi kana ndirini, tsoka dzangu dzakanga dzotsauka;
\s Makumbo angu akanga otedzemuka.
\p
\v 3 Nokuti ndakanga ndichigodora vana manyawi,
\s Pakuona kwangu kufara
\s kwavakaipa.
\p
\v 4 Nokuti havatambudziki pakufa kwavo;
\s Asi muviri wavo une simba.
\p
\v 5 Havana njodzi savamwe vanhu; Havatambudzwi savamwe vanhu
\p
\v 6 Saka kuzvikudza kwavo kwakafanana
\s noruketani pamitsipa yavo; Kumanikidza kunovafukidza senguo.
\p
\v 7 Meso avo anobuda nokukora; Zvavanofunga pamwoyo zvinofashamira;
\p
\v 8 Vanoseka, vachireva pakuipa kwavo zvinomanikidza vamwe;
\s Vanotaura vachizvikudza.
\p
\v 9 Vakataurira kudenga nemiromo yavo,
\s Ndimi dzavo dzinofamba-famba pasi.
\p
\v 10 Saka vanhu vake vanodzokera ikoko;
\s Vanosvinirwa mvura zhinji, mukombe uzere.
\p
\v 11 Zvino vanoti, "Mwari angaziva seiko?
\s Wokumusorosoro angava nokuziva here?"
\p
\v 12 Tarirai, ndizvo zvakaita vakaipa; Vanowedzera pfuma yavo vachingogara vasingatamburi.
\p
\v 13 Zvirokwazvo ndakanatsa mwoyo wangu pasina,
\s Nokushambidza maoko angu ndisina mhosva;
\p
\v 14 Nokuti ndakatambudzwa zuva rose,
\s Ndakarangwa mangwanani ose.
\p
\v 15 Kana ndaiti, ndichataura kudai;
\s Tarirai, ndainyengera rudzi
\s rwavana venyu.
\p
\v 16 Zvino ndakaramba ndichifunga kuti ndizvinzwisise,
\s Asi zvakandiremera kwazvo;
\p
\v 17 Kusvikira ndapinda panzvimbo tsvene yaMwari,
\s Ndikatarira kuguma kwavo.
\p
\v 18 Zvirokwazvo munovaisa panotedza;
\s Munovawisira pasi kuti vaparadzwe.
\p
\v 19 Haiwa, vanoparadzwa
\s kamwe-kamwe!
\p Vanopedzwa chose nezvinotyisa.
\v 2 Â° Sezvakarotwa, kana munhu apepuka;
\s Saizvozvo, Ishe, muchashora
\s mufananidzo wavo, kana muchimuka.
\p
\v 21 Nokuti mwoyo wangu wakachema,
\s Ndakabayiwa patsvo dzangu.
\p
\v 22 Ndakanga ndiri benzi, ndisingazivi chinhu;
\s Ndakanga ndakafanana nemhuka pamberi penyu.
\p
\v 23 Kunyange zvakadaro ndinoramba ndinemi;
\s Makabata ruoko rwangu rworudyi.
\p
\v 24 Muchandiperekedza nezano renyu,
\s Ndokuzondigamuchira pakubwinya.
\p
\v 25 Ndianiko kudenga, kana musimi?
\s Napasi hapana wandinoda kunze kwenyu.
\p
\v 26 Nyama yangu nomwoyo wangu zvinopera;
\s Asi Mwari ndiye dombo romwoyo wangu
\s nomugove wangu nokusingaperi.
\p
\v 27 Nokuti tarirai, vari kure nemi vachapera;
\s Makaparadza vose vakakusiyai noupombwe hwavo.
\p
\v 28 Kana ndirini, kuswedera pedyo naye nclizvo
\s zvinondifadza;
\s Ishe Mwari ndakamuita nhare yangu,
\s Kuti ndiparidze mabasa enyu ose.
